name: Koombanda

Introduction

This canyon is described in limited detail in Canyons Near Sydney by Rick Jamieson. Help the Australian canyoning community by contributing track notes to ropewiki.com

Quality

  • The canyon is rated 4 out of 10 on the Brennan Quality Scale.
  • David Noble rates the canyon 3 out of 5 for quality and Easy-Medium for difficulty.
